on in accordance with state law.(d) Monetary penalties collected under subsection (a) of this section shall be deposited into the division's operating fund to support the administration of the registry.(e) The division may pursue enforcement actions through the appropriate courts to ensure compliance with this article. Bill Status  | Bill Tracking  | Legacy WV Code  | Bulletin Board  | District Maps  | Senate Roster  | House Roster  | Live  | Blog  | Jobs  | Links  | Home This Web site is maintained by the West Virginia Legislature's Office of Reference & Information.  | Terms of Use | Webmaster | © 2025 West Virginia Legislature ** Print On Demand Name: Email: Phone: